{"tid":1584240,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工作不順政見不合與兒爭執　中年漢西貢墮樓亡","createTime":"2019-09-21T04:14:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T16:42:10.000Z","uid":20933,"like":36,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"00fe7dc1d23717dad548fe8eddc717340c1eed96","tid":1584240,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T04:14:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190921/s00001/2e8b21bab2fab3b8ea2659f544b732e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190921%2Fs00001%2F2e8b21bab2fab3b8ea2659f544b732e1.jpg&h=3b23a765&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n凌晨1時許，一名56歲男子在西貢翠塘花園墮樓，當場死亡。現場消息稱，上址保安報警指天台警鐘聲突然響起，未幾隨即發現有人從天而降，倒卧地上。<br />\n<br />\n救護人員接報到場檢查後，證實男子已死亡，毋須送院。警方調查後相信事件無可疑，亦未檢獲遺書，死因待驗屍確定。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，死者最近工作不如意決定退休，加上與兩名兒子政見不合，不時發生爭執，今晨由6樓寓所登上天台墮樓。"},{"pid":"6bfefe7777c491bf5a0c82debaefbf766eaa0d60","tid":1584240,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T04:14:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190921/s00001/1569029858956/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190921%2Fs00001%2F1569029858956%2F&d=ekRw3fL0jih6ME0SbOEd7z632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=a9a7162c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190921%2Fs00001%2F1569029858956%2F&h=fe344a7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190921/s00001/1569029858956/</a>"},{"pid":"30c8ab68dcfb5ab7884816dcb581815dd7bf02bc","tid":1584240,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T04:14:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">htt